"kind":"italic_en","text":"food sufficient to sustain life:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqowaAtN","text_ar":"اَقْوَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Einodahu quwtu","text_ar":"مَا عِنْدَهُ قُوتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapK","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapK","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiytu","text_ar":"قِيتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapK","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiytapu","text_ar":"قِيتَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has not a night's food sufficient to sustain life."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jad~u A@moriy^K fiY qaAy^itihi","text_ar":"جَدُّ ا@مْرِيٍ فِى قَايِتِهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", a prov., meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man's lot in life is"},{"kind":"text","text":"manifest"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his food."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Meyd.) ―         -b2-  See also 8, last sentence."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA","Msb"]}]}}